node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Seattle Kraken on September 07, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'SHUTOUT THE VIRUS PROOF OF VACCINATION REQUIRED'.

node.text: The #SeaKraken & @climatepledgearena will require all guests, ages 12+, attending Kraken games, concerts & events at Climate Pledge Arena to provide proof of vaccination to keep fans, staff, players & artists safe. Link in bio.

Reflecting the Pacific Northwest’s unique landscape, our Inaugural Season Patch aims to connect and honor our proximity to the sea, mountains and sky.

You can get your patch exclusively on jerseys beginning 9/15.
photo dump from the best summer ever! 🌞
